title: Person of Interest: Reese VS Nazis (I)
author: POI Fights
comment: Wow !  John Reese is an ultimate bad ass in this scene and episode !! This show was awesome !!
That moment you realize you're talking to a man that shoots cops and takes their badges.🤪
I live vicariously through Reese after a day of dealing with fools and jerks. Watching him administer his form of justice is a healthy therapy.
This had to be one of the greatest scenes from this show ! Incredible intense, threatening and cool  all at the same same time !!  Loved this series !
description: Fight Scene from S02 X 01: The Contingency
